heart attack and you died.

28:17.904 --> 28:19.072
I found you in the lab.

28:22.117 --> 28:24.452
You were already gone by
the time I got to you.

28:28.415 --> 28:30.583
I'm sorry I couldn't help.

28:36.256 --> 28:37.090
Hey, son.

28:38.383 --> 28:43.388
I've gone ahead and let
your news sink in, settle.

28:46.850 --> 28:48.059
Heart attack, huh?

28:50.228 --> 28:51.312
Yeah, your mother always told me

28:51.312 --> 28:53.231
I should lay off the beers and donuts.

28:56.818 --> 29:00.280
Well, it seems like a dream

29:00.280 --> 29:02.240
and I just need to wake up, but...

29:09.164 --> 29:14.169
Listen, Tom, I don't know
about surrogate loadin'.

29:16.755 --> 29:18.173
I can't have you doin' that.

29:19.090 --> 29:21.217
I don't know the side effects,
I mean, they could kill you.

29:29.726 --> 29:31.811
You gotta stop that, too.

29:38.234 --> 29:42.197
I'm not sure what you were talkin' about,

29:45.700 --> 29:48.787
the research, but

29:54.751 --> 29:56.252
I wish we completed it.

29:59.339 --> 30:02.050
I mean, we coulda saved so many families

30:03.468 --> 30:06.596
a lotta heartache, Tom, a lotta heartache.

30:10.433 --> 30:12.894
Ya know, I always wanted another kid.

30:12.894 --> 30:13.937
Mom, though, mm-mm.

30:16.105 --> 30:19.234
You were her full devotion.

30:21.110 --> 30:26.115
I mean, she wanted to give you
every opportunity possible.

30:30.703 --> 30:34.123
She wanted you to be an astronaut,

30:34.123 --> 30:36.459
a doctor, a musician all at the same time.

30:41.005 --> 30:42.048
I miss her, Tom.

30:44.259 --> 30:45.385
I really miss your mom.

30:47.971 --> 30:48.972
And I've missed you.

30:55.353 --> 30:56.396
I miss our family.

31:17.750 --> 31:19.961
Okay, almost got it here.

31:19.961 --> 31:21.504
Tom, why'd
you get this new camera?

31:21.504 --> 31:22.338
- Huh?

31:23.423 --> 31:27.677
Well, I got this new
camera because I wanna get

31:27.677 --> 31:29.554
all his shenanigans on video.

31:29.554 --> 31:30.889
He's growin' up quick.

31:30.889 --> 31:33.016
You know I don't
like havin' my picture taken.

31:33.016 --> 31:35.435
- It's not a picture, it's video.

31:36.853 --> 31:38.897
Hey, bud, get over here.

31:38.897 --> 31:41.107
Happy birthday, hon.

31:41.107 --> 31:42.775
I love you.

32:05.089 --> 32:05.924
One and two and three and four.

32:07.759 --> 32:08.801
- Tom.
- How many years ago

32:08.801 --> 32:09.802
.

32:09.802 --> 32:12.430
Come on, bud,
you're gonna have fun there.

32:14.515 --> 32:17.018
- This machine right here,
it's called a Scammer.

32:17.018 --> 32:18.686
It digitally scans your brain and-

32:18.686 --> 32:19.979
What's up, baby?

32:23.608 --> 32:24.984
This is your brain.

32:24.984 --> 32:26.402
I did you a favor.

32:26.402 --> 32:28.613
- Thank you, Dr. Davis.
- Believe this.

32:28.613 --> 32:30.073
Tom.

32:30.073 --> 32:32.742
- Tom!

32:54.305 --> 32:56.307
- Remind me again why you got it?

32:59.185 --> 33:00.603
Give it a rest, already.

33:04.857 --> 33:07.276
Mommy, you wanna play with me?

33:09.112 --> 33:11.572
Not now, buddy, Mommy's tired.

33:11.572 --> 33:12.740
Maybe later.

33:12.740 --> 33:14.033
- Why is she always tired?

33:14.033 --> 33:15.493
Can you come play with me?

33:15.493 --> 33:16.744
In a bit, okay.

33:20.248 --> 33:21.207
- Poor, baby doll.

33:22.667 --> 33:25.086
What was that boy's name?

33:25.086 --> 33:26.170
Who?

33:26.170 --> 33:28.089
The boy that was just in here.

33:28.965 --> 33:29.882
- Baby doll.

33:31.300 --> 33:32.135
No.

33:33.594 --> 33:35.013
- It's, um, it's...

33:38.891 --> 33:40.977
I don't know, what is it?

33:42.020 --> 33:42.895
It's Tom.

33:46.232 --> 33:47.233
Hey, kiddo.

33:49.027 --> 33:51.404
- Hey, Mom. How are you feeling?

33:51.404 --> 33:53.114
- You're a sweet little thing.

33:53.114 --> 33:55.158
What's your name, sweetie?

33:55.158 --> 33:57.535
- Sometimes you're silly, Mom. It's Tom.

33:58.578 --> 34:00.580
- That's a nice name. Where do you live?

34:01.497 --> 34:02.498
I live here.

34:03.624 --> 34:06.586
- No, we live here. Where do you live?

34:08.254 --> 34:10.089
Where are your parents?

34:15.762 --> 34:16.971
What's goin' on?

34:16.971 --> 34:17.805
It's okay, it's okay.

34:17.805 --> 34:19.015
- Who is he?

34:19.015 --> 34:19.849
Hey.

34:19.849 --> 34:21.976
Why is Mom asking where I live?

34:21.976 --> 34:23.770
Oh, she's just pretendin'.

34:24.645 --> 34:27.607
Ya know how you pretend when you play

34:27.607 --> 34:30.818
like you're a cowboy or a spaceman?

34:30.818 --> 34:32.945
- Yeah.
- That's what she's doin'.

34:32.945 --> 34:35.198
She's just pretendin'. Huh?

34:37.658 --> 34:38.743
Okay.

34:40.161 --> 34:41.954
Why don't you go in your room

34:41.954 --> 34:44.582
and I'll come in in a minute
and we could play, okay?

34:45.917 --> 34:46.918
Huh?
- Okay.

34:55.134 --> 34:57.178
- Hon, are you okay?

34:57.178 --> 34:58.638
Yeah, I'm okay, hon.

35:03.059 --> 35:04.644
Say goodbye to Mommy.

35:06.187 --> 35:08.523
But I don't
wanna leave my friends.

35:08.523 --> 35:10.358
I don't wanna go to a new school.

35:10.358 --> 35:11.192
Oh, come on, bud.

35:11.192 --> 35:12.693
You're gonna have fun there.

35:12.693 --> 35:15.071
- I don't wanna leave
Mom! I don't wanna go!

35:15.071 --> 35:17.657
Hey, if you don't
shut that door right now!

35:18.950 --> 35:20.076
And just stop it.

35:22.078 --> 35:23.955
How many times have we been over this?

35:27.542 --> 35:28.376
Bye, hon!

35:30.086 --> 35:32.672
- Bye. Say hi to your cousin.

35:32.672 --> 35:34.423
- I will.
- She was,

35:34.423 --> 35:35.591
she was too young.
- I'll be back

35:35.591 --> 35:36.425
in time for supper.

35:36.425 --> 35:39.137
- She was too young for that.

35:39.137 --> 35:40.555
Love you.

35:59.073 --> 36:00.324
Why didn't you?

36:04.996 --> 36:06.330
How was that possible?

36:07.999 --> 36:10.877
How did Mom lose her memory?
I mean, she was young.

36:15.882 --> 36:17.049
Why didn't you tell me?

36:19.510 --> 36:23.514
I mean, I hated you, Dad.

36:24.807 --> 36:26.434
I hated you for so long.

36:26.434 --> 36:29.562
Why didn't you tell me? I woulda helped.

36:30.605 --> 36:32.648
I coulda helped. I coulda done something.

36:36.360 --> 36:38.362
I'm not smart enough to
finish this without you.

36:38.362 --> 36:39.572
I don't know what to do.

36:53.211 --> 36:54.045
- Hey, man.

36:54.045 --> 36:54.879
- Hey.

36:54.879 --> 36:55.713
- Guess what?

36:55.713 --> 36:57.715
I just called Rocky and he's
ready to buy everything.

36:57.715 --> 36:59.675
The Mint, the Scammer, all the papers,

37:01.636 --> 37:04.222
I negotiated a pretty good
price, too, so that's good.

37:04.222 --> 37:05.056
- Cool.

37:05.932 --> 37:08.184
Look, man, he can have
the Mint and Scammer,

37:08.184 --> 37:11.896
but I gotta keep the research materials.

37:13.022 --> 37:16.275
- What in the name of science
are you talking about?

37:16.275 --> 37:17.777
I gotta continue my dad's research.

37:17.777 --> 37:19.028
He was trying to cure Alzheimer's.

37:19.028 --> 37:20.071
I mean, if it-
- You're pullin'

37:20.071 --> 37:20.905
my leg, right?

37:20.905 --> 37:21.948
Come on, just help me pack.

37:21.948 --> 37:24.075
Why don't you grab that.
- No, I'm serious, okay.

37:24.075 --> 37:25.493
I gotta finish my dad's work.

37:27.578 --> 37:30.039
- You realize that in
just a few short hours

37:30.039 --> 37:33.376
we can have more money than
Shelby Cobras have horsepower?

37:33.376 --> 37:35.920
But you're just being unreasonable.

37:35.920 --> 37:37.088
- Okay, fine.

37:37.088 --> 37:39.090
Gimme a few hours. I'll make
copies of the schematics.

37:39.090 --> 37:40.341
It'll be fine.
- No, we can't make

37:40.341 --> 37:41.384
a copy, okay?

37:41.384 --> 37:44.136
The price includes exclusivity, all right?

37:44.136 --> 37:45.012
Do you know what that means?

37:45.012 --> 37:45.846
- Yes I do.

37:45.846 --> 37:48.182
- No, apparently you don't, okay?

37:48.182 --> 37:49.558
Do you know why somebody buys

37:49.558 --> 37:51.894
a Bugatti Veyron Pur Sang for $3 million?

37:53.062 --> 37:54.897
There's only five of
them in the entire world.

37:54.897 --> 37:57.608
That means only five people own them.

37:57.608 --> 38:00.903
It's exclusive. Exclusivity.

38:00.903 --> 38:03.322
Look, will you stop?

38:03.322 --> 38:04.782
Okay, give it a rest.

38:04.782 --> 38:07.618
- Dude, you seriously cannot
be doing this right now.

38:07.618 --> 38:10.162
- Look, if I can't make any
copies, I'm not selling it.

38:10.162 --> 38:12.665
- This is dead end research
with no practical use.

38:12.665 --> 38:14.500
- My mom had Alzheimer's, okay?

38:17.878 --> 38:18.713
- Excuse me.

38:19.922 --> 38:22.591
- That's why my dad started all this, man.

38:22.591 --> 38:24.135
That's why I have to finish it.

38:25.803 --> 38:27.388
Okay, look, I'm sorry, Bruno.

38:27.388 --> 38:30.224
Hey, but if I can't make
copies, I can't sell it.

38:35.938 --> 38:39.817
- Okay, but how are you
gonna finish the research?

38:41.777 --> 38:42.778
- I don't know, I have his notes.

38:42.778 --> 38:45.489
I can use those. I thought
maybe you could help.

38:45.489 --> 38:46.866
- Yeah, what if I don't wanna help?

38:48.159 --> 38:49.785
- Then it's just me and the notes.

38:51.329 --> 38:54.415
Come on.

38:54.415 --> 38:57.501
- All right, fine, I'll help
you, but we do this my way.

38:57.501 --> 38:59.086
- That's fine. That's fine.

38:59.962 --> 39:00.796
Just,

39:02.256 --> 39:04.759
I need your help with something, okay?

39:04.759 --> 39:05.968
Just come on.

39:44.131 --> 39:45.841
Everything okay?

39:45.841 --> 39:48.386
- Oh yeah, yeah, yeah, just my mom.

39:50.346 --> 39:52.556
She wants to see if I
went to temple or not.

39:53.724 --> 39:55.351
- Didn't know you were religious.

39:57.645 --> 39:58.854
- Here and there. Beer?

40:00.022 --> 40:01.357
- Didn't know you drank either.

40:02.274 --> 40:03.109
- Here and there.

40:12.410 --> 40:14.995
- Hey man, let's have a little fun.

40:14.995 --> 40:15.996
- What kind of fun?

40:18.332 --> 40:19.500
- Look you can trust me, all right.

40:19.500 --> 40:20.709
I'm a research assistant.

40:20.709 --> 40:21.919
- Man, that just sounds
like a redneck saying,

40:21.919 --> 40:24.255
"Here, hold my beer and watch this."

40:24.255 --> 40:26.507
Look, I don't wanna fry my brain.

40:26.507 --> 40:27.383
- You won't!

40:28.259 --> 40:29.093
All right, how 'bout this?

40:29.093 --> 40:31.095
- Okay, if it makes you feel better,

40:31.095 --> 40:33.097
I can load your backup first.

40:33.097 --> 40:34.849
Man, I don't...

40:34.849 --> 40:35.891
- Dude, come on.

40:35.891 --> 40:37.518
If something goes wrong, it'll be my brain

40:37.518 --> 40:38.352
that gets fried, right?

40:38.352 --> 40:39.979
You've got nothing to lose.

40:39.979 --> 40:42.606
And if it works, then we
can load mine onto yours.

40:45.526 --> 40:48.154
Dude, I said no to a buttload of money

40:48.154 --> 40:49.613
just to help you out.

40:49.613 --> 40:52.158
Okay, and besides, you owe me.

40:52.158 --> 40:53.325
Remember that night you got super drunk

40:53.325 --> 40:54.910
and I stopped you from leaving?

40:54.910 --> 40:56.370
Do you remember what you said?

40:56.370 --> 40:57.872
- I owe you.
- Yeah.

40:57.872 --> 40:59.457
- All right, fine.

41:05.546 --> 41:07.006
You sure this is gonna work?

41:07.006 --> 41:08.841
- Yeah, man. I've done
it before, all right?

41:08.841 --> 41:10.217
It's just like drivin' a-

41:10.217 --> 41:12.553
- No car analogies, okay. I don't get 'em.

41:12.553 --> 41:13.637
Whose backup did you load?

41:13.637 --> 41:15.014
- Ya know, nobody important.

41:15.014 --> 41:16.599
- Ya know if you keep doin' that,

41:16.599 --> 41:18.267
you're gonna get down to your knuckles?

41:18.267 --> 41:21.854
All right,
drivers, start your engines.

41:21.854 --> 41:23.689
- What did I just say?

41:23.689 --> 41:25.774
- I'm from the Motor City, man. I'm sorry.

41:27.776 --> 41:28.652
Okay, here we go.

41:39.914 --> 41:41.290
This is Dr. Kirk Davis.

41:41.290 --> 41:43.542
Sorry I missed your call.

41:43.542 --> 41:46.337
Leave a name and number
and I will call you back.

41:51.967 --> 41:53.260
Bruno, calm down, man.

41:53.260 --> 41:55.012
- Why do you keep calling me Bruno?

41:56.180 --> 41:57.014
I'm Tom.

41:58.224 --> 41:59.058
- No.

42:05.773 --> 42:07.024
What's my social?

42:07.024 --> 42:07.858
- What?

42:07.858 --> 42:09.026
- What's my social?

42:09.026 --> 42:11.487
- 645-52-6465.

42:11.487 --> 42:13.822
- That's crazy. What's our
deepest, darkest secret?

42:13.822 --> 42:15.366
- Backin' up over Joshua's
cat and then telling him

42:15.366 --> 42:17.493
it ran away when he couldn't find it.

42:17.493 --> 42:18.953
- Tat on my left chest.

42:18.953 --> 42:20.788
- Okay, stop, stop, that's enough.

42:20.788 --> 42:21.664
- Look, I'm sorry, bro.

42:21.664 --> 42:25.626
What do I call you? This is crazy.

42:28.504 --> 42:29.797
- Dear Chu, love you lots.

42:31.006 --> 42:32.841
The tat on your left chest.

42:32.841 --> 42:34.218
Dear Chu, love you lots.

42:38.639 --> 42:41.433
- Man, cheers to takin'
care of our own selves.

42:41.433 --> 42:42.226
- Cheers.

42:51.110 --> 42:52.945
- All right, let's go
inside. There's more beer.

43:03.914 --> 43:05.874
This is Dr. Kirk Davis.

43:05.874 --> 43:07.710
Sorry I missed your call.

43:07.710 --> 43:10.212
Leave a name and number
and I will call you back.

43:24.226 --> 43:25.477
- Are you okay?

43:29.273 --> 43:30.524
No, hey. Bruno.

43:36.780 --> 43:37.615
Tom?

43:38.532 --> 43:40.868
What the hell are you doing?

43:42.786 --> 43:43.621
Yo. Whoa.

43:50.127 --> 43:55.132
What are you doing?

44:04.475 --> 44:06.393
- Hey, Bruno, what are you doing?

44:06.393 --> 44:08.562
Bruno, stop! Stop!

44:08.562 --> 44:09.396
Stop!

44:17.321 --> 44:18.155
What is going on?

44:18.155 --> 44:19.740
Are you okay?

44:19.740 --> 44:21.533
Tom, are you okay?

44:22.701 --> 44:24.453
Are you okay?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

44:24.453 --> 44:25.412
- What is going on?

44:25.412 --> 44:26.580
Why was Bruno tryin' to choke you?

44:26.580 --> 44:28.415
- It's not Bruno, it's me.

44:28.415 --> 44:30.334
- What?

44:30.334 --> 44:33.545
- I circuit loaded my memory onto Bruno.

44:33.545 --> 44:35.297
- Okay, I don't know what that means.

44:35.297 --> 44:37.341
- I put my memory on Bruno.

44:37.341 --> 44:39.093
Ya know that's stupid,

44:39.093 --> 44:41.261
even for a stupid person.

44:41.261 --> 44:42.262
Where is your dad?

44:42.262 --> 44:44.348
Does he know what you guys are up to?

44:44.348 --> 44:45.474
- He isn't here.

44:45.474 --> 44:47.017
Well, where is he?

44:47.017 --> 44:50.312
- He's at a hospital.

44:50.312 --> 44:52.106
He's outta town.

44:52.981 --> 44:53.982
He's doin' research.

44:55.442 --> 44:57.736
- That's odd, 'cause he
didn't say anything to me.

44:57.736 --> 44:59.446
- Let's just get him inside, okay.

45:01.490 --> 45:02.658
- Okay, ready?

45:02.658 --> 45:04.034
- One, two.
- Come on.

45:04.034 --> 45:05.661
- Okay.

45:05.661 --> 45:06.453
- I gotcha, come on.

45:06.453 --> 45:07.538
- All right, this way, this way.

45:07.538 --> 45:08.372
- Let's go, buddy.

45:08.372 --> 45:10.374
Come on.
- Okay.

45:10.374 --> 45:11.625
Okay.

45:23.345 --> 45:25.597
Hey.
- Good mornin'.

45:28.225 --> 45:30.769
Mm, that's how your dad checks my math.

45:33.897 --> 45:35.315
Yeah, he's awesome.

45:36.442 --> 45:37.568
Who's awesome?

45:40.696 --> 45:41.530
- Not you.

45:43.449 --> 45:45.117
- So, what happened last night?

45:46.952 --> 45:47.953
- Oh, shoot.

45:49.329 --> 45:52.791
Your buddy here will
give you the low down.

45:53.667 --> 45:55.961
I have to vamoose to class.

45:55.961 --> 45:59.256
But in the meantime, don't you guys

45:59.256 --> 46:01.300
go messin' with things
that you don't understand.

46:01.300 --> 46:02.134
You hear me?

46:02.134 --> 46:02.968
- Yes, ma'am.

46:02.968 --> 46:04.052
- Yes, ma'am.

46:05.137 --> 46:06.805
There's still hope for
you yet, tenderfoot.

46:09.641 --> 46:13.103
- So, what happened
last night? Did it work?

46:13.103 --> 46:14.229
- For an hour.

46:15.230 --> 46:17.191
- Okay, and then what?

46:17.191 --> 46:19.401
- The load went well,
but then you went crazy.

46:19.401 --> 46:21.737
I mean, you tried to attack me.

46:21.737 --> 46:23.864
- You mean you attacked yourself?

46:23.864 --> 46:25.449
- You threw things at me.

46:25.449 --> 46:27.993
You chased me around, you
put me in a choke hold.

46:27.993 --> 46:29.244
I mean, thank God Chloe showed up

46:29.244 --> 46:31.914
when she did and laid
you out with a shovel.

46:31.914 --> 46:34.374
- Okay, well, that explains this.

46:34.374 --> 46:36.293
God, she's got a mean swing.

46:36.293 --> 46:37.503
- Look, I'm not doin' that again, man.

46:37.503 --> 46:39.922
Okay, that scared the hell outta me.

46:39.922 --> 46:41.799
- Don't be such a downer, buddy, okay?

46:41.799 --> 46:44.384
Look at the shiny side. It worked.

46:45.928 --> 46:50.933
So, are you still against
selling this research?

46:51.016 --> 46:53.435
- She hit you a lot harder
than I expected, man.

46:56.188 --> 46:58.565
Do you not remember what
we discussed last night?

47:00.025 --> 47:01.693
I'm not selling. It's still a no.

47:07.324 --> 47:08.659
- It's fine.

47:08.659 --> 47:10.118
Just thought I'd ask again, ya know,

47:10.118 --> 47:11.370
just see what ya thought.

47:12.454 --> 47:13.956
Ya know what, this still kinda aches,

47:13.956 --> 47:17.334
so I think I'm gonna go get
it checked out at a doctors.

47:17.334 --> 47:18.585
- You want me to take you to the hospital?

47:18.585 --> 47:20.963
- No, no, no, no, no. It's fine.

47:20.963 --> 47:23.257
Just let me know where you'll be later.

47:23.257 --> 47:24.675
- The lab. Why?

47:24.675 --> 47:25.884
- Just wondering.

47:28.554 --> 47:29.388
- All right.

47:34.476 --> 47:35.561
How was that possible?

47:36.603 --> 47:39.439
How did Mom lose her memory?
I mean, she was young.

47:44.361 --> 47:46.154
Why didn't you tell me?

47:46.154 --> 47:48.615
I coulda helped. I coulda done something.

47:48.615 --> 47:50.576
I'm not smart enough to
finish this without you.

47:50.576 --> 47:51.785
I don't know what to do.

47:59.459 --> 48:01.503
Look, Dad, don't freak out, okay.

48:01.503 --> 48:03.338
Watch the video logs from yesterday,

48:03.338 --> 48:07.134
